text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to which women are
represented in the legislature and have an equal share of political power. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most equal).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
